OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear
OL,6,Fintervals and blustery showers this
OL,7,Fevening. The rest of the night will
OL,8,Fsee clear periods and a few showers.
OL,9,FOccasionally strong westerly winds,
OL,10,Feasing later on.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA few light showers in the
OL,13,Fmorning otherwise a dry bright day
OL,14,Fwith some sunny spells, lighter winds.
OL,15,FHigh cloud thickening later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
