OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDry
OL,6,Fand bright on Tuesday with some sunny
OL,7,Fspells, cloudier later with
OL,8,Fstrengthening southerly winds.
OL,9,FCloudier on Wednesday with chance of
OL,10,Frain or showers. Thursday sunny
OL,11,Fintervals and showers.
